Text.SourceString: I'm freaking out! We're officially married!//<portrait=blushing>I'm officially a husband now! How awesome is that?!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm freaking out! We're officially married!//<portrait=blushing>I'm officially a husband now! How awesome is that?!

Text.SourceString: Mom was there in spirit, you know... I could feel her presence with us.//<portrait=sad>Still, I really wish she could've been here in person.
Text.LocalizedString: Mom was there in spirit, you know... I could feel her presence with us.//<portrait=sad>Still, I really wish she could've been here in person.

Text.SourceString: Turns out, I don't have as much stuff as I thought. Moving in here was a breeze.//Thanks for all your help, baby.
Text.LocalizedString: Turns out, I don't have as much stuff as I thought. Moving in here was a breeze.//Thanks for all your help, baby.

Text.SourceString: Good morning, baby! I've prepared a special breakfast just for you. Dig in and enjoy!
Text.LocalizedString: Good morning, baby! I've prepared a special breakfast just for you. Dig in and enjoy!

Text.SourceString: I made this for you today, babe. Please enjoy!
Text.LocalizedString: I made this for you today, babe. Please enjoy!

Text.SourceString: You have such a captivating presence, both inside and out.//Come here, you... Let me give you a kiss.
Text.LocalizedString: You have such a captivating presence, both inside and out.//Come here, you... Let me give you a kiss.

Text.SourceString: Wow, babe, you are rocking that outfit! Fall hottie right here. Heck yeah!
Text.LocalizedString: Wow, babe, you are rocking that outfit! Fall hottie right here. Heck yeah!

Text.SourceString: I'm heading to Dad's after this.//He wanted some fish, so I figured I'd swing by and drop it off real quick before heading home.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm heading to Dad's after this.//He wanted some fish, so I figured I'd swing by and drop it off real quick before heading home.

Text.SourceString: Are you here to fish, baby?//Shall we reel in some adventures together?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you here to fish, baby?//Shall we reel in some adventures together?

Text.SourceString: This place, it's my absolute favorite.//Remember our wedding day right over there? Gosh, it was just perfect.
Text.LocalizedString: This place, it's my absolute favorite.//Remember our wedding day right over there? Gosh, it was just perfect.

Text.SourceString: It's been ages since I caught up with my sister. I think I'll go check on her later.
Text.LocalizedString: It's been ages since I caught up with my sister. I think I'll go check on her later.

Text.SourceString: Oops! Accidentally brought <NpcName>Lily</>'s notebook with me.//<portrait=normal>I'll make sure to return it tomorrow...or maybe next week.
Text.LocalizedString: Oops! Accidentally brought <NpcName>Lily</>'s notebook with me.//<portrait=normal>I'll make sure to return it tomorrow...or maybe next week.

Text.SourceString: Are you going to Dad's house anytime soon, babe? Can you drop it off?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you going to Dad's house anytime soon, babe? Can you drop it off?

Text.SourceString: I'm feeling too lazy to go out.//I think I'll just curl up in bed and read something. Wanna join me, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm feeling too lazy to go out.//I think I'll just curl up in bed and read something. Wanna join me, babe?

Text.SourceString: I'm feeling too lazy to go out.//I think I'll just curl up in bed and read something. Wanna join me, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm feeling too lazy to go out.//I think I'll just curl up in bed and read something. Wanna join me, babe?

Text.SourceString: I might go out for a little stroll and stretch my legs.
Text.LocalizedString: I might go out for a little stroll and stretch my legs.

Text.SourceString: What's the plan for today, babe? Anything exciting on the agenda?
Text.LocalizedString: What's the plan for today, babe? Anything exciting on the agenda?

Text.SourceString: The rain is pouring like crazy out there. Stay safe and be extra careful today, babe.
Text.LocalizedString: The rain is pouring like crazy out there. Stay safe and be extra careful today, babe.

Text.SourceString: Living here with you is pure bliss. It's so peaceful and calm—I can actually hear my own thoughts.
Text.LocalizedString: Living here with you is pure bliss. It's so peaceful and calm—I can actually hear my own thoughts.

Text.SourceString: My favorite farmer, on duty!
Text.LocalizedString: My favorite farmer, on duty!

Text.SourceString: Taking a little break, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: Taking a little break, babe?

Text.SourceString: Our farm is so beautiful, thanks to your hard work and creative touch.
Text.LocalizedString: Our farm is so beautiful, thanks to your hard work and creative touch.

Text.SourceString: Got any dinner requests, babe? I'm thinking tacos tonight.
Text.LocalizedString: Got any dinner requests, babe? I'm thinking tacos tonight.

Text.SourceString: I learned how to cook from Dad, and I gotta admit, I kinda enjoy it. As a kid, I always wanted to be a cook like him.
Text.LocalizedString: I learned how to cook from Dad, and I gotta admit, I kinda enjoy it. As a kid, I always wanted to be a cook like him.

Text.SourceString: But hey, life had different plans for me. The sea has completely stolen my heart...and you...
Text.LocalizedString: But hey, life had different plans for me. The sea has completely stolen my heart...and you...

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Lily</> likes staying at that haunted villa... I mean, uh, that place is colder than the North Pole even in the middle of Summer.//100% ghost hideout!
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Lily</> likes staying at that haunted villa... I mean, uh, that place is colder than the North Pole even in the middle of Summer.//100% ghost hideout!

Text.SourceString: Thinking about what Dad went through when...well, you know, when we lost Mom...it's tough.
Text.LocalizedString: Thinking about what Dad went through when...well, you know, when we lost Mom...it's tough.

Text.SourceString: Now that I've found my better half and get to live with you every day, <PlayerName>$Player</>, I never want to imagine a life without you...ever.
Text.LocalizedString: Now that I've found my better half and get to live with you every day, <PlayerName>$Player</>, I never want to imagine a life without you...ever.

Text.SourceString: Babe, I found a cherry shirt in my drawer this morning. Is it yours or <NpcName>Lily</>'s?
Text.LocalizedString: Babe, I found a cherry shirt in my drawer this morning. Is it yours or <NpcName>Lily</>'s?

Text.SourceString: I love you, <PlayerName>$player</>. Please never leave me.
Text.LocalizedString: I love you, <PlayerName>$player</>. Please never leave me.

Text.SourceString: I don't know what I would do without you...
Text.LocalizedString: I don't know what I would do without you...

Text.SourceString: I'm gonna crack open some windows. This house has a slight garlic scent...//<portrait=normal>Not that I mind. I actually like the smell of garlic.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm gonna crack open some windows. This house has a slight garlic scent...//<portrait=normal>Not that I mind. I actually like the smell of garlic.

Text.SourceString: I might just chill here for a little while, babe.
Text.LocalizedString: I might just chill here for a little while, babe.

Text.SourceString: I like how my room stays the same...it's like I've never left.
Text.LocalizedString: I like how my room stays the same...it's like I've never left.

Text.SourceString: Our house should be spotless now! I gave it a good cleaning.//What do you think? Husband of the year, yeah?
Text.LocalizedString: Our house should be spotless now! I gave it a good cleaning.//What do you think? Husband of the year, yeah?

Text.SourceString: I'll be home as soon as I'm done here, babe.//If you're hungry, please go ahead and eat first, okay?
Text.LocalizedString: I'll be home as soon as I'm done here, babe.//If you're hungry, please go ahead and eat first, okay?

Text.SourceString: I can hear the pups from here. Ha ha! They're singing along with me.
Text.LocalizedString: I can hear the pups from here. Ha ha! They're singing along with me.

Text.SourceString: Come here, baby...gimme a kiss.
Text.LocalizedString: Come here, baby...gimme a kiss.

Text.SourceString: In this day and age, people can be so greedy.//We're always chasing after more and more and more.//<portrait=sad>It’s sad, really.
Text.LocalizedString: In this day and age, people can be so greedy.//We're always chasing after more and more and more.//<portrait=sad>It’s sad, really.

Text.SourceString: There was a time I used to freak out about not having a 'real job' or taking the same beaten path as my sis.//<portrait=surprised>But hey, not anymore!
Text.LocalizedString: There was a time I used to freak out about not having a 'real job' or taking the same beaten path as my sis.//<portrait=surprised>But hey, not anymore!

Text.SourceString: I am who I am, and there’s nothing wrong with that.//<portrait=happy>People may call me boring, but I know myself better.//<portrait=normal>I’m not boring or unmotivated… I’m laid-back.
Text.LocalizedString: I am who I am, and there’s nothing wrong with that.//<portrait=happy>People may call me boring, but I know myself better.//<portrait=normal>I’m not boring or unmotivated… I’m laid-back.

Text.SourceString: Anyone can catch legendary fish at sea with enough skill.//<portrait=normal>They’re hard to find, but not impossible.
Text.LocalizedString: Anyone can catch legendary fish at sea with enough skill.//<portrait=normal>They’re hard to find, but not impossible.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Sunny</> is a big name around here.//Dude used to chase down those legendary monster fish like it was his job!
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Sunny</> is a big name around here.//Dude used to chase down those legendary monster fish like it was his job!

Text.SourceString: I’m not actively hunting for legendary fish.//I don’t see the appeal.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m not actively hunting for legendary fish.//I don’t see the appeal.

Text.SourceString: Gotta hand it to <NpcName>Betty</>, though.//She's out there making sure our feathered friends don't go hungry.
Text.LocalizedString: Gotta hand it to <NpcName>Betty</>, though.//She's out there making sure our feathered friends don't go hungry.

Text.SourceString: Wealth isn’t everything, babe. Don’t waste your life chasing it.
Text.LocalizedString: Wealth isn’t everything, babe. Don’t waste your life chasing it.

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> seems to be deep in thought.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> seems to be deep in thought.]

Text.SourceString: For a while, I tried making a living as a truck driver, but it can get pretty lonely on the road.
Text.LocalizedString: For a while, I tried making a living as a truck driver, but it can get pretty lonely on the road.

Text.SourceString: I guess being away from family for too long just isn’t for me.//<portrait=normal>The pay was good, though.
Text.LocalizedString: I guess being away from family for too long just isn’t for me.//<portrait=normal>The pay was good, though.

Text.SourceString: The thing about playing the guitar is that you have to feel it in your gut first.//<portrait=normal>Then it will flow out through the melody.
Text.LocalizedString: The thing about playing the guitar is that you have to feel it in your gut first.//<portrait=normal>Then it will flow out through the melody.

Text.SourceString: Feeeeel it, <PlayerName>$player</>.
Text.LocalizedString: Feeeeel it, <PlayerName>$player</>.

Text.SourceString: This is usually the season when a lot of fish eggs hatch.//I had to release a lot of fish back to the ocean the other day because they were too small.
Text.LocalizedString: This is usually the season when a lot of fish eggs hatch.//I had to release a lot of fish back to the ocean the other day because they were too small.

Text.SourceString: Doesn’t all this new life make you feel inspired, <PlayerName>$player</>? The birth of new creatures also means the birth of new ideas.
Text.LocalizedString: Doesn’t all this new life make you feel inspired, <PlayerName>$player</>? The birth of new creatures also means the birth of new ideas.

Text.SourceString: I’m looking forward to going to the Cherry Blossom Festival with you.//I’ve got a couple of new songs I want to play.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m looking forward to going to the Cherry Blossom Festival with you.//I’ve got a couple of new songs I want to play.

Text.SourceString: You hear that, baby? I only wish I could sing as great as the birds. So carefree and beautiful.
Text.LocalizedString: You hear that, baby? I only wish I could sing as great as the birds. So carefree and beautiful.

Text.SourceString: The island is so alive with music, <PlayerName>$player</>.//The crashing of the waves, the chirping of the birds, and even the rustling of the new leaves come together to make this beautiful Spring music.
Text.LocalizedString: The island is so alive with music, <PlayerName>$player</>.//The crashing of the waves, the chirping of the birds, and even the rustling of the new leaves come together to make this beautiful Spring music.

Text.SourceString: It’s so much nicer to go out there and fish now.//I don’t have to stand in the freezing cold anymore.
Text.LocalizedString: It’s so much nicer to go out there and fish now.//I don’t have to stand in the freezing cold anymore.

Text.SourceString: I caught a tuna the other day, so I guess we’re entering Summer now.
Text.LocalizedString: I caught a tuna the other day, so I guess we’re entering Summer now.

Text.SourceString: The Summer breeze feels different on my face… A little saltier than Spring, if you want to know.
Text.LocalizedString: The Summer breeze feels different on my face… A little saltier than Spring, if you want to know.

Text.SourceString: I see seals, turtles, all sorts of wild critters swimming to shore in the Summer.//<portrait=normal>I chat them up sometimes, just for a bit of fun.
Text.LocalizedString: I see seals, turtles, all sorts of wild critters swimming to shore in the Summer.//<portrait=normal>I chat them up sometimes, just for a bit of fun.

Text.SourceString: This heat is getting to me, babe. Think we should take a dip?//I might if you're up for it…
Text.LocalizedString: This heat is getting to me, babe. Think we should take a dip?//I might if you're up for it…

Text.SourceString: A nice cold milk sounds tempting, but it's not the best idea.//Tends to upset my stomach, and we've still got the whole day ahead of us.
Text.LocalizedString: A nice cold milk sounds tempting, but it's not the best idea.//Tends to upset my stomach, and we've still got the whole day ahead of us.

Text.SourceString: I wouldn't recommend sailing too far out in this heat. Might run into a storm at sea…//Just a word of caution.
Text.LocalizedString: I wouldn't recommend sailing too far out in this heat. Might run into a storm at sea…//Just a word of caution.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Sunny</> is the defending champion in the swimming contest. //<portrait=surprised>I'm still shocked how he can swim that fast at his age!
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Sunny</> is the defending champion in the swimming contest. //<portrait=surprised>I'm still shocked how he can swim that fast at his age!

Text.SourceString: I've just noticed how radiant you look in the Summer heat. It suits you, babe.
Text.LocalizedString: I've just noticed how radiant you look in the Summer heat. It suits you, babe.

Text.SourceString: I don’t know why all the songs I’m writing are super sad lately. Here’s what I wrote yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know why all the songs I’m writing are super sad lately. Here’s what I wrote yesterday.

Text.SourceString: “The lifeless leaves have left my life.” What a downer.
Text.LocalizedString: “The lifeless leaves have left my life.” What a downer.

Text.SourceString: I'm still singing and writing songs, babe, but it's a bit tougher for me to do in the Fall.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm still singing and writing songs, babe, but it's a bit tougher for me to do in the Fall.

Text.SourceString: You know how I know it’s Fall? I caught plenty of cod yesterday!
Text.LocalizedString: You know how I know it’s Fall? I caught plenty of cod yesterday!

Text.SourceString: I woke up today, and I didn’t feel too good. Then I looked at the calendar.//This is the week when we lost Mom…
Text.LocalizedString: I woke up today, and I didn’t feel too good. Then I looked at the calendar.//This is the week when we lost Mom…

Text.SourceString: Summer was cool. I caught plenty of tuna. The Beach Shack was pretty happy…//But today...today's a different story.
Text.LocalizedString: Summer was cool. I caught plenty of tuna. The Beach Shack was pretty happy…//But today...today's a different story.

Text.SourceString: Fall's not really my season, babe.//Having you by my side though, it makes it so much better. Thank you...
Text.LocalizedString: Fall's not really my season, babe.//Having you by my side though, it makes it so much better. Thank you...

Text.SourceString: Fishing wasn’t that great this week, but still managed to land a yellowfin tuna. Must be Winter settling in!
Text.LocalizedString: Fishing wasn’t that great this week, but still managed to land a yellowfin tuna. Must be Winter settling in!

Text.SourceString: Are you excited for the New Year’s Eve Festival, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: Are you excited for the New Year’s Eve Festival, babe?

Text.SourceString: Setting sail in Winter can be a risky business, but with the right training and precautions, it’s manageable.
Text.LocalizedString: Setting sail in Winter can be a risky business, but with the right training and precautions, it’s manageable.

Text.SourceString: Do you think it's too cold for ice cream? Maybe, but I wouldn’t refuse one if it came my way!
Text.LocalizedString: Do you think it's too cold for ice cream? Maybe, but I wouldn’t refuse one if it came my way!

Text.SourceString: Certain fish tend to avoid the chill of Winter. They up and swim away to warmer waters.
Text.LocalizedString: Certain fish tend to avoid the chill of Winter. They up and swim away to warmer waters.

Text.SourceString: Like which ones? Hmm… let's see. Rainbow fish are Fall fish, not Winter. Cobia, too, I think.
Text.LocalizedString: Like which ones? Hmm… let's see. Rainbow fish are Fall fish, not Winter. Cobia, too, I think.

Text.SourceString: I hope this New Year offers you a fresh start, baby.//Whether that means having another go at your dreams or maybe setting some new ones.
Text.LocalizedString: I hope this New Year offers you a fresh start, baby.//Whether that means having another go at your dreams or maybe setting some new ones.

Text.SourceString: Making peace with myself was the hardest thing I’ve ever done.//Now I take every day as it comes, with an extra dose of gratitude.
Text.LocalizedString: Making peace with myself was the hardest thing I’ve ever done.//Now I take every day as it comes, with an extra dose of gratitude.

Text.SourceString: For me, it's a bit of a tradition to bring fresh fish to the Cherry Blossom Festival.//Dad would always bring his smoked salmon.
Text.LocalizedString: For me, it's a bit of a tradition to bring fresh fish to the Cherry Blossom Festival.//Dad would always bring his smoked salmon.

Text.SourceString: And I’ll open the festival with a song of my own.//<portrait=happy>Drives the crowds wild.
Text.LocalizedString: And I’ll open the festival with a song of my own.//<portrait=happy>Drives the crowds wild.

Text.SourceString: *yawns* I’m still tired from singing all day yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: *yawns* I’m still tired from singing all day yesterday.

Text.SourceString: Oh, I’m happy singing here, <PlayerName>$player</>.//I don’t need some fancy label to tell me how to live.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, I’m happy singing here, <PlayerName>$player</>.//I don’t need some fancy label to tell me how to live.

Text.SourceString: Today I wanna focus on my soul and just feed my brain some thoughts.
Text.LocalizedString: Today I wanna focus on my soul and just feed my brain some thoughts.

Text.SourceString: My throat's a bit scratchy, babe…might've overdone it with the banana fritters last night.
Text.LocalizedString: My throat's a bit scratchy, babe…might've overdone it with the banana fritters last night.

Text.SourceString: Either that, or I’m developing a pollen allergy. Hmm…
Text.LocalizedString: Either that, or I’m developing a pollen allergy. Hmm…

Text.SourceString: I might go fishing at our farm pond.//I'm curious about what fish species might be lurking in there.
Text.LocalizedString: I might go fishing at our farm pond.//I'm curious about what fish species might be lurking in there.

Text.SourceString: Not today, though. Maybe when the water is a bit cooler.
Text.LocalizedString: Not today, though. Maybe when the water is a bit cooler.

Text.SourceString: Why do I feel like there’s a new bug in town every Summer?
Text.LocalizedString: Why do I feel like there’s a new bug in town every Summer?

Text.SourceString: I could really go for some ice cream right now.
Text.LocalizedString: I could really go for some ice cream right now.

Text.SourceString: I'm taking the day off for the Beach Cleanup Festival. Should we go together, babe?
Text.LocalizedString: I'm taking the day off for the Beach Cleanup Festival. Should we go together, babe?

Text.SourceString: Season changes don't bother me. I'm still doing my thing...fishing, singing...loving you.
Text.LocalizedString: Season changes don't bother me. I'm still doing my thing...fishing, singing...loving you.

Text.SourceString: I don’t pay much attention to the calendar. Too constricting.//I gauge the seasons by the fish I catch.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t pay much attention to the calendar. Too constricting.//I gauge the seasons by the fish I catch.

Text.SourceString: Let’s see what I can come up with for a Fall song.
Text.LocalizedString: Let’s see what I can come up with for a Fall song.

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> seems to be deep in thought.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> seems to be deep in thought.]

Text.SourceString: Happy harvest season, baby!
Text.LocalizedString: Happy harvest season, baby!

Text.SourceString: Wait a sec... I'm getting some Fall melody inspiration. Dum~ Dum~
Text.LocalizedString: Wait a sec... I'm getting some Fall melody inspiration. Dum~ Dum~

Text.SourceString: Singing in the rain? Now that is an idea.
Text.LocalizedString: Singing in the rain? Now that is an idea.

Text.SourceString: I don’t know how I feel about that. It just seems… Cold.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t know how I feel about that. It just seems… Cold.

Text.SourceString: Money was never really a thing for me. My dad was a fisher his whole life, and Mom was a diver.//We had a pretty great life overall.
Text.LocalizedString: Money was never really a thing for me. My dad was a fisher his whole life, and Mom was a diver.//We had a pretty great life overall.

Text.SourceString: Growing up, I knew some people who had a lot more than we did, but they weren’t half as happy.
Text.LocalizedString: Growing up, I knew some people who had a lot more than we did, but they weren’t half as happy.

Text.SourceString: I almost slipped on the ice this morning. You be careful out there, baby!
Text.LocalizedString: I almost slipped on the ice this morning. You be careful out there, baby!

Text.SourceString: One of my favorite things about Winter is all the festive decorations. They make the town feel so alive.
Text.LocalizedString: One of my favorite things about Winter is all the festive decorations. They make the town feel so alive.

Text.SourceString: Making peace with myself was the hardest thing I’ve ever done.//Now I take every day as it comes, with an extra dose of gratitude.
Text.LocalizedString: Making peace with myself was the hardest thing I’ve ever done.//Now I take every day as it comes, with an extra dose of gratitude.

Text.SourceString: I don’t travel a lot. Like, travel for leisure, you know. But I’ve gone places for work, and I’ve seen things.
Text.LocalizedString: I don’t travel a lot. Like, travel for leisure, you know. But I’ve gone places for work, and I’ve seen things.

Text.SourceString: But being away from you and the family for too long just doesn't sit right with me.
Text.LocalizedString: But being away from you and the family for too long just doesn't sit right with me.

Text.SourceString: My boat isn’t the most reliable in the rain, so I better stick to fishing on sunny days.
Text.LocalizedString: My boat isn’t the most reliable in the rain, so I better stick to fishing on sunny days.

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]

Text.SourceString: My boat isn’t the most reliable in the rain, so I better stick to fishing on sunny days.
Text.LocalizedString: My boat isn’t the most reliable in the rain, so I better stick to fishing on sunny days.

Text.SourceString: It gets dark so early lately.
Text.LocalizedString: It gets dark so early lately.

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is in a rush.]

Text.SourceString: One of my favorite things about Winter is all the festive decorations. They make the town feel so alive.
Text.LocalizedString: One of my favorite things about Winter is all the festive decorations. They make the town feel so alive.

Text.SourceString: It gets dark so early lately.
Text.LocalizedString: It gets dark so early lately.

Text.SourceString: It gets dark so fast in Winter.
Text.LocalizedString: It gets dark so fast in Winter.

Text.SourceString: I’m in the mood for something crunchy.
Text.LocalizedString: I’m in the mood for something crunchy.

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is singing – better not bother him.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> is singing – better not bother him.]

Text.SourceString: Any song requests, baby? I'm all ears.
Text.LocalizedString: Any song requests, baby? I'm all ears.

Text.SourceString: This gig isn’t really banking the big bucks for me. But it isn’t always about the money, ya know?//<portrait=happy>It’s about doing something that you love.
Text.LocalizedString: This gig isn’t really banking the big bucks for me. But it isn’t always about the money, ya know?//<portrait=happy>It’s about doing something that you love.

Text.SourceString: Are you here for me, babe?//<portrait=happy>Grab a seat, I’m about to sing. You won’t want to miss this.
Text.LocalizedString: Are you here for me, babe?//<portrait=happy>Grab a seat, I’m about to sing. You won’t want to miss this.

Text.SourceString: I had this mega satisfying meal that <NpcName>Frank</> made yesterday.//<portrait=normal>Not sure if he's got leftovers, but give it a shot if he does.
Text.LocalizedString: I had this mega satisfying meal that <NpcName>Frank</> made yesterday.//<portrait=normal>Not sure if he's got leftovers, but give it a shot if he does.

Text.SourceString: Oy, <NpcName>Frank</>! Make one of those super meals for my baby right here, will ya?
Text.LocalizedString: Oy, <NpcName>Frank</>! Make one of those super meals for my baby right here, will ya?

Text.SourceString: I sing to chill out my soul. Hopefully, it hits the same notes for anyone who listens.
Text.LocalizedString: I sing to chill out my soul. Hopefully, it hits the same notes for anyone who listens.

Text.SourceString: I already delivered some of my catch to the Beach Shack.//Aiming to hook a few more before the day's out.
Text.LocalizedString: I already delivered some of my catch to the Beach Shack.//Aiming to hook a few more before the day's out.

Text.SourceString: Day fishing's my jam.//<portrait=normal>Don't need to cast out under the moonlight.
Text.LocalizedString: Day fishing's my jam.//<portrait=normal>Don't need to cast out under the moonlight.

Text.SourceString: Breaking habits is a tough game.//But taking it one step at a time, especially with you by my side, makes it more manageable.
Text.LocalizedString: Breaking habits is a tough game.//But taking it one step at a time, especially with you by my side, makes it more manageable.

Text.SourceString: Nothing in life's a walk in the park, <PlayerName>$player</>.//But taking it step by step helps a lot!
Text.LocalizedString: Nothing in life's a walk in the park, <PlayerName>$player</>.//But taking it step by step helps a lot!

Text.SourceString: I’m lucky I got out when I could.//<portrait=sad>I didn’t know what would happen to my family or me if I…
Text.LocalizedString: I’m lucky I got out when I could.//<portrait=sad>I didn’t know what would happen to my family or me if I…

Text.SourceString: Never mind.
Text.LocalizedString: Never mind.

Text.SourceString: Always felt like I was waiting for something. No clue what.//<portrait=sad>It felt like torture.
Text.LocalizedString: Always felt like I was waiting for something. No clue what.//<portrait=sad>It felt like torture.

Text.SourceString: Now I’m not waiting anymore.//<portrait=happy>I’m living…with you.
Text.LocalizedString: Now I’m not waiting anymore.//<portrait=happy>I’m living…with you.

Text.SourceString: [<NpcName>Theo</> seems to be concentrating.]
Text.LocalizedString: [<NpcName>Theo</> seems to be concentrating.]

Text.SourceString: Sure are a lot of books in the library…
Text.LocalizedString: Sure are a lot of books in the library…

Text.SourceString: Do you think anyone’s read all these books?
Text.LocalizedString: Do you think anyone’s read all these books?

Text.SourceString: I really like this positive glow that you bring, <PlayerName>$player</>. Always puts a smile on my face.
Text.LocalizedString: I really like this positive glow that you bring, <PlayerName>$player</>. Always puts a smile on my face.

Text.SourceString: Dad once said that all any parent ever wants is for their children to be happy.//I think he was right. I think that’s what my mother would’ve wanted for <NpcName>Lily</> and me.
Text.LocalizedString: Dad once said that all any parent ever wants is for their children to be happy.//I think he was right. I think that’s what my mother would’ve wanted for <NpcName>Lily</> and me.

Text.SourceString: Make no mistake, <PlayerName>$player</>. I’m going to pursue happiness. I won’t disappoint my mother.
Text.LocalizedString: Make no mistake, <PlayerName>$player</>. I’m going to pursue happiness. I won’t disappoint my mother.

Text.SourceString: I’m not <NpcName>Theo</> the fisher today. Today I am <NpcName>Theo</>, the singer!
Text.LocalizedString: I’m not <NpcName>Theo</> the fisher today. Today I am <NpcName>Theo</>, the singer!

Text.SourceString: Sing a ballad with me, baby?
Text.LocalizedString: Sing a ballad with me, baby?

Text.SourceString: If I had a keg, I'd be making strawberry juice all year round, just for you.//I might even start growing strawberries for it.
Text.LocalizedString: If I had a keg, I'd be making strawberry juice all year round, just for you.//I might even start growing strawberries for it.

Text.SourceString: Wait a sec… Do we need a keg or a jar for making juice?//<portrait=concerned>Hmm… One of those, anyway. You get what I mean.
Text.LocalizedString: Wait a sec… Do we need a keg or a jar for making juice?//<portrait=concerned>Hmm… One of those, anyway. You get what I mean.

Text.SourceString: Letting go of Mom has been so hard. She was still so young, it just doesn't feel fair.//She had a full life ahead of her, and it was taken so abruptly. We were just kids.
Text.LocalizedString: Letting go of Mom has been so hard. She was still so young, it just doesn't feel fair.//She had a full life ahead of her, and it was taken so abruptly. We were just kids.

Text.SourceString: …I never got to say goodbye.
Text.LocalizedString: …I never got to say goodbye.

Text.SourceString: Spending too much time in crowds can be draining for me.//It saps my creativity, that's why I only perform on weekends.
Text.LocalizedString: Spending too much time in crowds can be draining for me.//It saps my creativity, that's why I only perform on weekends.

Text.SourceString: But being with you... It rejuvenates me.
Text.LocalizedString: But being with you... It rejuvenates me.

Text.SourceString: Spring is extra pretty with you around.
Text.LocalizedString: Spring is extra pretty with you around.

Text.SourceString: Use extra blankets tonight, will you?//I don’t want you to get cold.
Text.LocalizedString: Use extra blankets tonight, will you?//I don’t want you to get cold.

Text.SourceString: Winter isn’t so bad now that you’re around.
Text.LocalizedString: Winter isn’t so bad now that you’re around.

Text.SourceString: My neck feels a bit stiff. Ugh… I guess I slept on it funny last night, but I didn’t think it would last this long.
Text.LocalizedString: My neck feels a bit stiff. Ugh… I guess I slept on it funny last night, but I didn’t think it would last this long.

Text.SourceString: I slept on my stomach.//<portrait=annoyed>Usually, my neck sorts itself out in a couple of hours. Never taken this long before.
Text.LocalizedString: I slept on my stomach.//<portrait=annoyed>Usually, my neck sorts itself out in a couple of hours. Never taken this long before.

Text.SourceString: Don’t worry too much if you wake up with a sore neck. It’ll get better in time.//The thing is… Neck is neck. It gets sore once in a while.
Text.LocalizedString: Don’t worry too much if you wake up with a sore neck. It’ll get better in time.//The thing is… Neck is neck. It gets sore once in a while.

Text.SourceString: You look extra cute today!//Spring suits you.
Text.LocalizedString: You look extra cute today!//Spring suits you.

Text.SourceString: You look extra cute today!//Fall looks good on you.
Text.LocalizedString: You look extra cute today!//Fall looks good on you.

Text.SourceString: Sleeping is great… It’s even better when it’s snowing out.//Sleep soothes the mind. It’s an important part of the day.
Text.LocalizedString: Sleeping is great… It’s even better when it’s snowing out.//Sleep soothes the mind. It’s an important part of the day.

Text.SourceString: The red boat there, it's more than just a vessel to me. It's my father's legacy.//He spent countless hours on these waters, just like I do now.
Text.LocalizedString: The red boat there, it's more than just a vessel to me. It's my father's legacy.//He spent countless hours on these waters, just like I do now.

Text.SourceString: I remember how proud Dad was when he put those lampions up on the boat. Said it was to light the way home after a long day's catch.//That's what he told me when I was five.
Text.LocalizedString: I remember how proud Dad was when he put those lampions up on the boat. Said it was to light the way home after a long day's catch.//That's what he told me when I was five.

Text.SourceString: Now that I'm an adult, I think he had the lampions up because that's the only decorations we had.//<portrait=sad>Lampions and family pictures, not much else.
Text.LocalizedString: Now that I'm an adult, I think he had the lampions up because that's the only decorations we had.//<portrait=sad>Lampions and family pictures, not much else.

Text.SourceString: I may have given my boat a fresh coat of paint, but that red color is sacred.//<portrait=normal>It's a symbol of our family's history, and I couldn't bear to change it.
Text.LocalizedString: I may have given my boat a fresh coat of paint, but that red color is sacred.//<portrait=normal>It's a symbol of our family's history, and I couldn't bear to change it.

Text.SourceString: There's something about being out here on the open sea, that makes me feel closer to Mom.//<portrait=sad>Like she's still with me in some way.
Text.LocalizedString: There's something about being out here on the open sea, that makes me feel closer to Mom.//<portrait=sad>Like she's still with me in some way.

Text.SourceString: Some folks might say it's just a boat, but to me, it's a piece of who I am.//<portrait=happy>And I plan to pass it down to our kids one day, so they can understand what it means to be a fisherman and carry on our family traditions.
Text.LocalizedString: Some folks might say it's just a boat, but to me, it's a piece of who I am.//<portrait=happy>And I plan to pass it down to our kids one day, so they can understand what it means to be a fisherman and carry on our family traditions.

Text.SourceString: Mom...the ocean claimed her.//<portrait=concerned>But when I sing here, by the shore, I like to believe that somehow, she can hear me.
Text.LocalizedString: Mom...the ocean claimed her.//<portrait=concerned>But when I sing here, by the shore, I like to believe that somehow, she can hear me.

Text.SourceString: I can tell you one thing, <PlayerName>$Player</>: when things get hard and you feel like you can't handle it, try letting go.//<portrait=happy>Believe that, at the end of the day, things will work out as they should.
Text.LocalizedString: I can tell you one thing, <PlayerName>$Player</>: when things get hard and you feel like you can't handle it, try letting go.//<portrait=happy>Believe that, at the end of the day, things will work out as they should.

Text.SourceString: It helped me, and it might help you too.
Text.LocalizedString: It helped me, and it might help you too.

Text.SourceString: You're doing great today, baby!//Remember that progress, no matter how small, is still progress.
Text.LocalizedString: You're doing great today, baby!//Remember that progress, no matter how small, is still progress.
